cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning, specifically studying the internal representations of a deep network and using clustering algorithms to extract visual concepts. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves unsupervised learning (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL) in the form of semantic part annotations.
